The Safest & Most Competitive Global Sourcing Event Is Now

Almost ready and raring to go. The year’s first and only live, in-person food & beverage sourcing event kicks off this Sunday, 21 Feb for five incredible days of fast-moving trade talks, deal signings and culinary inspirations.

2,500 companies from 85 countries across 20 halls. 60+ chefs including Michelin Starred culinary masters. 110+ speakers including renowned business leaders, government heads and food innovators. Soon all will unite face-to-face in the safest space.

Get ready to get ahead.

Visit Now : https://www.gulfood.com/
